snippet: Starbucks is planning a chain that will sell high-end coffee from around the world, and its branding will be steps removed from its mass-market cousin.
abstract: Starbucks is opening Starbucks Reserve Roastery and Tasting Room in Seattle, flagship of planned chain that will sell high-end coffees from around the world; company's reach into higher-end market is another sign that coffee consumption in the United States is growing only modestly.
lead_paragraph: Starbucks is planning a chain that will sell high-end coffee from around the world, and its branding will be steps removed from its mass-market cousin.

headline.main: Starbucks, Facing a Saturated Market, Looks to the High End
headline.print_headline: With Market Saturated, Starbucks Looks to High End
